Package: REDCapExtractR
Title: Extract REDCap data using API for use in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Totterdell", , "jatotterdell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extract REDCap data into and R session, and optionally write to a database.
    The aim is consistency rather than flexibility for the API requests.
